        <section class="teacher-content">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12">
                        <h1>Meet your faculty at Illinois State University</h1>
                        <p>Your faculty at Illinois State University love teaching in a diverse and welcoming community. They create an engaging environment in the classroom and are passionate about sharing their research and experience with students. This is why they are the perfect mentors to guide you toward success in the professional world.</p>
<p>Your professors will make sure that you have a rewarding learning experience and feel prepared to graduate. Our hands-on teaching will include:</p>
<ul>
<li>an interactive teaching environment that incorporates cultural concepts</li>
<li>a traditional approach to teaching subjects</li>
<li>small class sizes of no more than 18 students for English language teaching</li>
</ul>

                    </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                            
