<div class="testimonial-gallery container">
    <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="imagebox" data-target="dr-john">
                                    <img src="https://ctfimages.intoglobal.com/xw2h6mjophtz/2syOSP0FSBPOhFD7CL22qH/89fa9285a7c4907c0728a20fd34d7544/INTO_ISU_John-R.-Baldwin.jpg?w=500" class="category-banner img-fluid">
                            <div class="imagebox-desc">
                                <h5>Dr. John - Professor, School of Communication</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="quote-container">
                            <div class="quote-diamond"></div>
                            <div class="quote quote-mobile">
                                    <h2>Dr. John, Professor, School of Communication</h2>
                                <p>“I love the way that Illinois State focuses on education of students, with a student-centered focus. I love teaching, and I especially enjoy working with international students. I always learn new things from them about the beautiful and complex world we live in.</p>
<p>I have two recommendations for international students. First, go visit your professor during office hours—they usually want to know you and help you! Also, get outside of the classroom. Join a club; get out and around; make friends with Americans or students from other cultures. That is the best way to really understand a culture.”</p>
;
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="imagebox" data-target="dr-klaus">
                                    <img src="https://ctfimages.intoglobal.com/xw2h6mjophtz/2r9iZgG9BmRqcOzbEmGSmh/dcf47e6ebfbd08660c1346fdae99ffeb/INTO_ISU_Klaus-Schmidt.jpg?w=500" class="category-banner img-fluid">
                            <div class="imagebox-desc">
                                <h5>Dr. Klaus - Professor of Technology</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="quote-container">
                            <div class="quote-diamond"></div>
                            <div class="quote quote-mobile">
                                    <h2>Dr. Klaus, Professor of Technology</h2>
                                <p>“I have worked with international students for many years and in many capacities. As an international student at one time myself, I believe and understand the challenges and aspirations international students may have.  I started working for Illinois State University almost 20 years ago, and I am thrilled to be part of the ISU family.  I feel that ISU has moved toward greater international activities, and I am proud to be part of these activities.</p>
<p>From my experience as an international student, I learned that it is so very important to learn and understand the local community - to be included in the activities in the community on-campus, but also off-campus. Learning the American way of life can be so valuable and enriching.&quot;</p>
;
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="imagebox" data-target="dr-krzysztof">
                                    <img src="https://ctfimages.intoglobal.com/xw2h6mjophtz/5XtjizLY4YW7eBwerCWYer/ce082ae505643d57237b14abe997236c/INTO_ISU_Krzysztof-Ostaszewski.jpg?w=500" class="category-banner img-fluid">
                            <div class="imagebox-desc">
                                <h5>Dr. Krzysztof - Actuarial Program Director</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="quote-container">
                            <div class="quote-diamond"></div>
                            <div class="quote quote-mobile">
                                    <h2>Dr. Krzysztof, Actuarial Program Director</h2>
                                <p>“Our Actuarial Program is recognized as a Center of Actuarial Excellence by the Society of Actuaries. We also won the Casualty Actuarial Society’s University Award in 2016 and 2019. Illinois State is also a Global Center of Insurance Excellence. No other university in the world has all of these recognitions.</p>
<p>We are a place of serious study and hard work. We welcome students from all over the world. We will strive to educate you to be successful, mature, knowledgeable and competent actuarial professionals. </p>
<p>We are also a place where students are very important. Your dreams, your goals, your life, matter to us greatly. Come and study with us, to experience a uniquely supportive environment.”</p>
;
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="" class="quote-desktop">
                        <div class="col-12 quote-text">
                            <div class="quote-text-value" id="dr-john">
                                    <h2>Dr. John, Professor, School of Communication</h2>
                                <p>
                                    <p>“I love the way that Illinois State focuses on education of students, with a student-centered focus. I love teaching, and I especially enjoy working with international students. I always learn new things from them about the beautiful and complex world we live in.</p>
<p>I have two recommendations for international students. First, go visit your professor during office hours—they usually want to know you and help you! Also, get outside of the classroom. Join a club; get out and around; make friends with Americans or students from other cultures. That is the best way to really understand a culture.”</p>

                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="" class="quote-desktop">
                        <div class="col-12 quote-text">
                            <div class="quote-text-value" id="dr-klaus">
                                    <h2>Dr. Klaus, Professor of Technology</h2>
                                <p>
                                    <p>“I have worked with international students for many years and in many capacities. As an international student at one time myself, I believe and understand the challenges and aspirations international students may have.  I started working for Illinois State University almost 20 years ago, and I am thrilled to be part of the ISU family.  I feel that ISU has moved toward greater international activities, and I am proud to be part of these activities.</p>
<p>From my experience as an international student, I learned that it is so very important to learn and understand the local community - to be included in the activities in the community on-campus, but also off-campus. Learning the American way of life can be so valuable and enriching.&quot;</p>

                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="" class="quote-desktop">
                        <div class="col-12 quote-text">
