                                <p>
                                    <p>“Our Actuarial Program is recognized as a Center of Actuarial Excellence by the Society of Actuaries. We also won the Casualty Actuarial Society’s University Award in 2016 and 2019. Illinois State is also a Global Center of Insurance Excellence. No other university in the world has all of these recognitions.</p>
<p>We are a place of serious study and hard work. We welcome students from all over the world. We will strive to educate you to be successful, mature, knowledgeable and competent actuarial professionals. </p>
<p>We are also a place where students are very important. Your dreams, your goals, your life, matter to us greatly. Come and study with us, to experience a uniquely supportive environment.”</p>

                                </p>
