                <section class="teacher-content">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Who should I go to for help?</h2>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <p>Support doesn't end when you step outside of the classroom. Your tutors at Illinois State University are here to answer any academic questions you have. Free tutoring services help you understand the prompt for your English essay, stay on track with homework assignments and get subject-specific research help. Count on your tutors to:</p>
<ul>
<li>meet with you one-on-one or in group sessions</li>
<li>give you guidance with test prep, including GMAT and GRE</li>
<li>choose the right classes to stay on track for graduation</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Additional support on campus also includes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>a dedicated Academic Advisor to give you career guidance</li>
<li>help with cultural adaptation and language skills through the Language Partners program</li>
<li>workshops to help you with specialized topics</li>
</ul>

                        <a href="/en/universities/illinois-state-university/studying/student-support" class="l-cta cta nav-item-content">More about student support</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
